at|^^|cp||at|^b1. The only way for responder to force to game is to bid the 4th suit (analogous to 4th suit forcing). Any other bid by responder is not game forcing. If responder does not bid the 4th suit, and opener has a hand strong enough to force to game (18+), then it is up to opener to take charge and force to game.|
